        <h2 class="text-[#131615] text-[22px] font-bold leading-tight tracking-[-0.015em] px-4 pb-3 pt-5">What is Integral Ecology?</h2>
        <p class="text-[#131615] text-base font-normal leading-normal pb-3 pt-1 px-4">
                            Integral ecology recognizes the interconnectedness of all living beings and ecosystems, emphasizing the need for a unified approach to address environmental
                            challenges. It integrates ecological, social, economic, and cultural dimensions to foster sustainable and harmonious relationships between humans and nature.
                        </p>
        <h2 class="text-[#131615] text-[22px] font-bold leading-tight tracking-[-0.015em] px-4 pb-3 pt-5">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-[#131615] text-base font-normal leading-normal pb-3 pt-1 px-4">
